      "Create strong passphrases with EFF's new random number generators!",
    link: {
      name: "Github",
      url: "https://github.com/yplog/EFF-Dice-Generated-Passphrases",
    },
    tags: ["python", "pickledb"],
    image: "https://www.eff.org/files/banner_library/dice-1.png",
    isArchived: true,
  },
  {
    title: "Picate",
    description: "Lets you search for photos and save them to your favorites.",
